---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="GDPR operational readiness for technology companies. Access the EU market with confidence and protect personal data.">
  <HeroSection
    headline="GDPR Operational Readiness for Technology Companies"
    subheadline="Access the EU market with confidence. Protect personal data. Demonstrate accountability."
    ctaText="Get Started"
    ctaHref="/about"
  />

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>Why GDPR Matters</h2>
    <p>The General Data Protection Regulation is the world's most comprehensive data protection framework. For technology companies serving EU customers or processing EU residents' data, GDPR compliance is not optional &mdash; it's the price of market access.</p>
    <div class="value-grid">
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Access the EU Market</h3>
        <p>GDPR compliance is non-negotiable for serving EU customers. Without it, enterprise buyers, partners, and distributors in the EU and EEA will not engage.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Avoid Significant Penalties</h3>
        <p>Fines up to &euro;20 million or 4% of global annual turnover &mdash; whichever is higher &mdash; make GDPR enforcement among the most consequential in any regulatory regime.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Meet Processor Obligations</h3>
        <p>If you process data on behalf of EU controllers, GDPR compliance is contractually required. Controllers will audit your practices and demand documented accountability.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Enable Cross-Border Operations</h3>
        <p>Proper transfer mechanisms &mdash; SCCs, adequacy decisions, binding corporate rules &mdash; enable global data flows without legal exposure.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>How We Help</h2>
    <p>Four service packages designed to meet you where you are in your compliance journey.</p>
    <div class="service-overview-grid">
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Readiness Sprint</h3>
        <p>Scope, assess, and plan in 2&#8211;4 weeks</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Remediation Program</h3>
        <p>Close gaps and build your evidence machine</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Audit Support</h3>
        <p>Expert coordination during audit fieldwork</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Continuous Compliance</h3>
        <p>Stay audit-ready year-round</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
    <p>Whether you're entering the EU market for the first time or strengthening an existing privacy program, we can help you build an accountability framework that satisfies regulators and customers alike.</p>
    <a href="/about" class="cta-button">Let's Talk</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .service-overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card {
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .service-overview-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-heading);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem var(--spacing-page);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
